Designation: Director of Token Marketing **I'm Hiring!**
Description: The official token of the Quidd ecosystem. A fungible utility token built on Ethereum, QUIDD is the cornerstone of a new, cooperative economic system that aligns the interests of collectors, creators, and developers. Join us on Telegram! For early access, prizes, and the latest news as it happens. Read Lightpaper.
Summary: " Quidd Token - The official token of the Quidd ecosystem . Buy and sell officially licensed digital collectibles from more than 325 brands . Quidd is available on the world's first digital collectible marketplace . QuidD is the cornerstone of a new, cooperative economic system that aligns the interests of collectors, creators, and developers . The QUIDD Token will be offered for sale only outside of the United States to non-U.S. persons, pursuant to the provisions of Regulation S of the U.S Securities Act of 1933, as amended . The Quidd token is a fungible utility token built on the ERC-20 ."}

Designation: Fulfillment Operations Logistics Director at Promontory MortgagePath LLC
Description: SCHEDULE A DEMO. Promontory MortgagePath LLC. delivers flawless digital mortgage and fulfillment solutions driven by innovative tech, driving down the cost and time required to originate a mortgage. We invest in compliance, technology and human resources so you can focus on what matters - helping your borrowers achieve their homeownership dreams.
Summary: Promontory MortgagePath LLC delivers flawless digital mortgage and fulfillment solutions driven by innovative tech . We invest in compliance, technology and human resources so you can focus on what matters – helping your borrowers achieve their homeownership dreams . Our proprietary point-of-sale (POS) lending platform, Borrower Wallet, offers an intuitive, collaborative and consistent borrower experience across any device . Our mortgage fulfillment solutions have been proudly endorsed by:‹‚How Mortgage Fulfillment Outsourcing WorksYour customer submits their application information via your website . We process, underwrite and close – all in your name. Then, our team prepares the closed loan for sale to your secondary market investors or for portfolio retention .'}

Designation: Director Of Compliance - AML Compliance at Prometheum
Description: Prometheum will provide users the rails to create compliant digital asset securities through an easy-to-use platform that removes the difficulty of creating securities on a blockchain. Digital asset securities issued outside of Prometheum's ecosystem will also be able to leverage our marketplace and technology. Trading back and front end.
Summary: Prometheum leverages blockchain technology to provide infrastructure for compliant issuance, trading and settlement of digital asset securities . Our wallet technology ensures that blockchain-native assets can be moved in and out of users’ brokerage accounts in a secure, compliant and streamlined manner . No money or consideration is being solicited by the information in this or any other communication and, if sent, money will not be accepted and will be withdrawn before any such offer can be accepted by the SEC, accepted before the SEC accepted it, or withdrawn it will be promptly returned to the market . Digital asset securities issued outside of the ecosystem will also be able to leverage our marketplace and technology .'}

Designation: Non Executive Director | Advisor
Description: Hire faster and fairer with the world's first Smart Interviewer. With a two-stage chat and video-based interview process, our Smart Interviewer platform automates your hiring process, disrupting bias and delivering ultimate candidate satisfaction. Our AI is ethical, explainable, and backed by peer-reviewed scientific research.

Designation: Talent Acquisition and Experience Lead @Parcl
Description: Parcl is a blockchain-based real estate platform that allows users to invest in a digital square foot of physical real estate in the most lucrative neighborhoods around the U.S. Build your dream real estate portfolio and trade your favorite neighborhoods just like you would Crypto assets. There's no minimum investment, low transaction fees, and high liquididty.
Summary: Parcl - Your Global Real Estate Portfolio.Join the waitlist . Our Price Feed mimics the behavior of real world real estate markets and gives users access to price exposure without the burdens of owning or transacting hard assets. Parcl allows you to gain exposure to entire cities like Manhattan or Miami, and specific neighborhoods like Tribeca or Brickell. The global real estate market is dominated by moguls with deep pockets - investors like investors like you are locked out of the types of the opportunities you want to trade in . Parcl is a digital real estate platform that lets you gain exposure with no minimum investment, high liquidity, and low transaction fees .'}

Designation: Hiring for SAP consultants, React js, Project Managers
Description: We offer support for your sales force and force.com applications. Our experts have experience making lightning components, custom applications and integration to other cloud platforms including SAP. Vibhathi has experienced software developers delivering full-stack experience on .NET, Java, salesforce, force.com and Javascript.
Summary: Vibhathi Labs Inc Offering support in USA, Europe and India . Full Stack Software Development on.NET/Java stack, ReactJS or Angular as well as Sales Force development . SAP functional consultants that can assist your users, interact with developers on changes, monitor workflows, produce reports and help with patches/upgrades . SAP Fiori & UI5 Services for your apps enhance the app user experience and performance using Fiori . SAP Technical Services can be deployed to address your technical needs in your SAP infrastructure including on S4/HANA. SAP Functional Services can assist users and help developers with updates and patches/upsets .'}

Designation: Co-founder Console.xyz (We're hiring!)
Description: Founded in January 2019, International Trust Machines Corporation (ITM) provides both a blockchain scaling solution and blockchain-enabled ICs. In this era of exponential growth in IoT devices and the expanding prevalence of blockchain ledger technology, ITM addresses the issue of convergence in blockchain technology and the Internet of Things ...
Summary: " ITM addresses the issue of convergence in blockchain technology and the Internet of Things with a practical and scalable solution . With its patented Merkle Tree technologies and blockchain IC solutions, ITM effectively eliminates bottlenecks in the blockchain trilemma . ITM provides the first-ever solution for clearing millions of off-chain data with only a single main-chain transaction, ensuring immutability for the assurance of trustworthy and legitimate information . The easiest way to connect your application or data to Ethererum at zero cost, for efficiency and trust . Get Started with ITM's Bitcoin-based notary service. Get Started in January 2019."}
